            "data": "All 3 changes applied to `dashboard.html`:\n\n1. **CSS** — 14 new rules (`.search-select`, `.search-results`, `.search-opt`, `.search-ava`, `.field-label-row`, `.field-link`, `.drawer-back`) inserted after `.field-row`, before `/* Toast */`.\n\n2. **PROVIDERS + NewPatientDrawer** — `PROVIDERS` array with 3 providers and a full `NewPatientDrawer` component (first/last name, DOB, phone, email, insurance, minor checkbox with conditional guardian field, consent checkbox, back arrow header, disabled save button) inserted before `NewAppointmentDrawer`.\n\n3. **NewAppointmentDrawer replaced** — Patient field now uses a typeahead `search-select` with avatar initials + name + ID in the dropdown, plus a \"+ New patient\" link that opens the `NewPatientDrawer` sub-drawer. Provider field uses the same typeahead pattern filtering the `PROVIDERS` array showing name + operatory. On new patient save, auto-selects the patient and returns to the appointment drawer. All other fields unchanged."
