t context pre-loaded (e.g., auto-open the relevant tab).\n- b. **New appointment-focused workspace** — A dedicated layout with the appointment at the center: patient header, tooth chart, SOAP notes editor, status actions, and treatment plan — all visible without tabs.\n- c. **Other** — Describe what you envision."
